racle-vault/ (multiple agent backups with Rule 6 learnings)\n\n**Soul-Brews-Studio repos:**\n- /shrimp-oracle.wt-1/docs/identity-system.md\n- /two-rivers-oracle/ψ-backup/memory/traces/2026-02-28/0853_rule-6-transparency.md\n- /opensource-nat-brain-oracle/ψ-backup/memory/retrospectives/\n- /oracle-vault/ (mirror of laris-co vault)\n\n**Primary Sources in Vault (most authoritative):**\n- /Users/nat/Code/github.com/laris-co/oracle-vault/github.com/laris-co/nat-s-agents/ψ/memory/resonance/rule-transparency.md\n- /Users/nat/Code/github.com/laris-co/oracle-vault/github.com/laris-co/nats-brain-oracle/ψ/memory/learnings/oracle/rule-6-transparency.md\n- /Users/nat/Code/github.com/laris-co/oracle-vault/github.com/laris-co/mother-oracle/ψ/memory/learnings/2026-02-19_rule-6-transparency-oracle-nev.md"}
